content: User added the following context for their work at CommerceHub: They implemented revised merchandising services sales efforts that resulted in a doubling of the client base and a 70% YoY revenue spike. They developed a tiered structure of engagement focusing on qualification, implementing an entry-level PoV to reduce time spent on non-converting clients. This contributed to the YoY growth. They revamped sales collateral and marketing materials for the program. They also closed a seven-figure revenue deal with Ashley Furniture, a multibillion-dollar retailer.
